---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

---

<BaseLayout title="Problems I'm Working On — Nivedita Pandey">
  <div class="problems-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Problems I'm Working On</h1>
      <p class="page-description">
        The questions I keep returning to — across applied AI, institutions, and the infrastructure that shapes how people live.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="page-banner">
      <img
        src="/images/about-ai.png"
        alt="At a technology conference"
        class="page-banner-img"
      />
    </div>

    <section class="problem-domain">
      <h2 class="domain-title">Applied AI</h2>
      <p class="domain-intro">
        How do emerging AI capabilities translate into real-world impact — in healthcare, governance, and everyday commerce?
        These are not just technical problems. They require institutional design, trust-building, and context-specific deployment.
      </p>

      <div class="subdomains">

        <details class="subdomain">
          <summary>
            <span class="subdomain-title">Healthcare</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="subdomain-content">
            <p>
              How can voice-based and conversational AI improve healthcare access in low-literacy populations?
              What does responsible deployment look like when patient data meets AI interfaces?
              How do you build AI tools that work within the constraints of India's fragmented healthcare system?
            </p>
            <p class="placeholder-note">More detail coming soon. <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> if you're working on this.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="subdomain">
          <summary>
            <span class="subdomain-title">Governance</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="subdomain-content">
            <p>
              How do governments and regulated institutions build genuine capacity for AI adoption — not just technical training,
              but organizational readiness, governance frameworks, and change management at scale?
              What does responsible AI adoption look like in public institutions with legacy infrastructure and accountability constraints?
            </p>
            <p class="placeholder-note">More detail coming soon. <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> if you're working on this.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="subdomain">
          <summary>
            <span class="subdomain-title">Retail & Consumer Goods</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="subdomain-content">
            <p>
              How do consumer brands use AI to build deeper market understanding and accelerate go-to-market decisions —
              especially in complex, multi-market contexts?
            </p>
            <p class="placeholder-note">More detail coming soon. <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> if you're working on this.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="subdomain">
          <summary>
            <span class="subdomain-title">Finance</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="subdomain-content">
            <p>
              To be added.
            </p>
            <p class="placeholder-note">More detail coming soon. <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> if you're working on this.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="subdomain">
          <summary>
            <span class="subdomain-title">Elder Care</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="subdomain-content">
            <p>
              How can AI tools improve coordination and quality of care for elderly populations — particularly in the context
              of NRI families managing parents' healthcare across distance and fragmented providers?
              What's the right balance between technology and human care?
            </p>
            <p class="placeholder-note">More detail coming soon. <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> if you're working on this.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="problem-domain coming-soon">
      <h2 class="domain-title">More Coming Soon</h2>
      <p class="domain-intro">
        Other problem areas I'm actively thinking through — on Human-Computer Interaction, Mental Health &amp; Neuroscience,
        and Institutional Change — will be added here.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="page-footer">
      If you're working on any of these problems, I'd like to hear from you.
      <a href="mailto:np@niveditapandey.com">np@niveditapandey.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .problems-page {
    max-width: 750px;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .page-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .page-banner {
    width: 100%;
    height: 740px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-banner-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    display: block;
  }

  .problem-domain {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .problem-domain:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .domain-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .domain-intro {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .subdomains {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .subdomain {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .subdomain:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .subdomain summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .subdomain summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .subdomain summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .subdomain[open] summary::after {
    content: '−';
  }

  .subdomain-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .subdomain summary:hover .subdomain-title {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .subdomain-content {
    padding: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .subdomain-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .subdomain-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .placeholder-note {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .placeholder-note a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .coming-soon .domain-intro {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .page-footer {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .page-footer a {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .page-banner {
      height: 220px;
    }
  }
</style>
